 }}&lt;/ref&gt; In April 1838, the name was officially changed to ''The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter Day Saints''.&lt;ref&gt;{{Citation |last=Smith |first=Joseph, Jr |authorlink=Joseph Smith, Jr |journal=Elders' Journal of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter Day Saints |volume=1 |issue=4 |date=August 1838 |pages=52 |url=http://www.solomonspalding.com/docs/eldjur04.htm |title=Special Collections |postscript=.}}, {{Citation
