==Software==

===Sogou Pinyin===
[[Sogou Pinyin]] is a popular Chinese Pinyin input method editor developed by Sogou, a Chinese search engine.
It is also available on-line without installation, through a so-called &quot;cloud input method&quot;.

===Google Pinyin===
Please refer to the term [[Google Pinyin]].

