      <text xml:space="preserve">{{redirect|Canadian Pacific}}
{{Infobox SG rail
| railroad_name=Canadian Pacific Railway
| logo_filename=Canadian_Pacific_Logo_1996.png
| logo_size=100
| system_map=Canadian Pacific System Railmap.PNG
| map_size=300
| map_caption=Canadian Pacific system map  (does not include [[Dakota, Minnesota and Eastern Railroad|DM&amp;E]] trackage)
| marks=CP
| locale=[[Canada]] with branches to [[United States]] cities: [[Chicago]], [[Minneapolis]] and [[New York City]]
